The '''2400 yacht''' was a model of luxury [[Yacht/Legends|yacht]] that was manufactured and sold by [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]] as a luxury model. Resembling the later [[Personal Luxury Yacht 3000/Legends|Personal Luxury Yacht 3000]], it was fifty [[Meter/Legends|meters]] long, with a thin [[Hull/Legends|hull]] and two outrigger propulsion pods, one on each side. ''[[Love Commander]]'' was one such ship.

